oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Kinsall's daughter Lucinda pinning the Silver Oak Leaves pin on her father
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of Lt. Col. J.Y. Kinsall with his two year old daughter Lucinda. Lucinda is standing on a desk while pinning the Silver Oak Leaves pin on Kinsall, who recently made Lieutenant Colonel. Photograph was originally printed in "The Strata Courier" newspaper based out of Mountain Home, Idaho.
